			<p class="breadcrumb"><a href="../../../index.html">ENCS Home</a> &gt; <a href="../index.php">News &amp; events</a> &gt; <a href="index.php">Faculty Magazine</a> &gt; <a href="../issue.php_q_Fall_y_2011">Fall 2011</a> &gt;</p>
